<codeline><highlight class="normal">NWNX_Weapon_SetWeaponSpecializationFeat<sp/>|<sp/>Associate<sp/>a<sp/>weapon<sp/>specialization<sp/>feat<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>weapon<sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">NWNX_Weapon_SetEpicWeaponFocusFeat<sp/>|<sp/>Associate<sp/>an<sp/>epic<sp/>weapon<sp/>focus<sp/>feat<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>weapon<sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">NWNX_Weapon_SetEpicWeaponSpecializationFeat<sp/>|<sp/>Associate<sp/>an<sp/>epic<sp/>weapon<sp/>specialization<sp/>feat<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>weapon<sp/></highlight></codeline>
