<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">The<sp/>NWNX_Weapon_SetOption<sp/>function<sp/>can<sp/>be<sp/>used<sp/>to<sp/>define<sp/>the<sp/>attack<sp/>and<sp/>damage<sp/>bonusses<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>Greater<sp/>Weapon<sp/>Focus<sp/>Feats<sp/>and<sp/>Greater<sp/>Weapon<sp/>Specialization<sp/>Feats<sp/>respectively.<sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Example<sp/>for<sp/>Critical<sp/>Event<sp/>Script</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">This<sp/>script<sp/>just<sp/>print<sp/>some<sp/>info<sp/>to<sp/>the<sp/>log<sp/>and<sp/>then<sp/>bypass<sp/>the<sp/>devastating<sp/>critcial<sp/>50%<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>time.<sp/>You<sp/>have<sp/>to<sp/>set<sp/>your<sp/>script<sp/>with<sp/>NWNX_Weapon_SetDevastatingCriticalEventScript(&quot;name_of_your_script&quot;)<sp/>(in<sp/>the<sp/>OnModuleLoad<sp/>script<sp/>for<sp/>example)</highlight></codeline>
